.incwave file format
#TYPE# : plane, dipol, etc.
#PARAM1#
#PARAM2#
#PARAM3#
...
#PARAMN#

Example plane wave:
########
Plane #type
WaveLength #in terms of meters
DirX #forward direction
DirY
DirZ
PolX #polarization, must be orthogonal to forward direction
PolY
PolZ
PhaseOriginX # the point where the phase of the incoming plane wave is PhaseOffset
PhaseOriginY
PhaseOriginZ
PhaseOffset # between 0 and 2pi
########